                        <li>Check your email for any additional verification requests from Stripe</li>
                        <li>Review your creator dashboard and upcoming topics</li>
                        <li>Start planning content for your funded topics</li>
                        <li>Refresh this page in a few minutes to check status</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
                    <a href="stripe_onboarding.php?creator_id=<?php echo $creator_id; ?>" class="btn">üîÑ Check Status</a>
                    <a href="dashboard.php" class="btn btn-primary">üìä Creator Dashboard</a>
                </div>
            <?php endif; ?>

            <div style="margin-top: 25px; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                <p><strong>üîí Secure:</strong> All payment information is handled securely by Stripe</p>
